entry.def: A spinner is a cricketer who makes the ball spin when he or she bowls it so that it changes direction when it hits the ground or the bat.
A spinner is a person who makes thread by spinning.

means.word_mean: 1. someone who spins (who twists fibers into threads)
2. board game equipment that consists of a dial and an arrow that is spun to determine the next move in the game
3. fisherman's lure; revolves when drawn through the water
